# OnlineJobs.ph — Job application workflow

Read skill: [`.cursor/skills/onlinejobs-apify/SKILL.md`](../skills/onlinejobs-apify/SKILL.md).

## When the agent should act

- User mentions **OnlineJobs.ph**, **OJP**, remote PH jobs, or “find laravel/react jobs”
- User says **apply to #N** after a search result table
- User asks for **cover letter**, **submission message**, or **CV for this job**

## Search → apply flow

1. Use MCP `search_onlinejobs` or `search_onlinejobs_fullstack_ai`.
2. Show the returned Markdown table as-is (includes row numbers).
3. On apply: call `create_job_application` with fields from the **Apply reference (JSON)** block for that row.
4. Report folder path and remind user to open `submission.txt` + attach CV.

## Application folder convention

```text
job-applications/YYYY-MM-DD_Slug-Title_Slug-Company/
  job-info.json
  submission.txt
  CARLLOUISMANUEL-CV.docx
```

- `job-applications/` is **gitignored** — local only.
- Do not commit application folders.

## Tailored CV tagline

Infer from job title unless user passes `tailored_tagline`:

| Title signals | Tagline |
|---------------|---------|
| react, node, typescript | Senior React Developer · Full-Stack Engineer |
| laravel, php | Senior PHP/Laravel Engineer · Full-Stack Developer |
| ai, openai, llm, claude | Full-Stack Engineer · AI Integration Specialist |
| flutter, mobile | Full-Stack Engineer · Flutter & Mobile Developer |
| (default) | Senior Full-Stack Engineer · AI Integration Specialist |

CV is generated via `apply_canva_cv_design.py --output ... --tagline ... --no-backup`.

## Cover message rules

- Professional, outcome-focused tone (see [`v3-copy.mdc`](v3-copy.mdc)).
- Reference Metrobank, GoAutoDial, ABS-CBN only as **public** portfolio proof — no confidential details.
- **Never** mention Tahanan, HOA platform, or `tahanan.org` in submission text.
- Do not invent salary or employer facts not in the listing.

## Before user submits

- Suggest they skim `submission.txt` and personalize one sentence if needed.
- Note any `[CONFIRM: ...]` metrics still in `src/external-config.js` / generated CV if relevant.

## MCP troubleshooting

- If `onlinejobs-apify` errors: check `APIFY_API_TOKEN` in Cursor MCP settings and restart Cursor.
- Apify runs can take **2–5 minutes** — warn user when searching.
- CV generation requires `python-docx` (used by `Office-Word-MCP-Server/apply_canva_cv_design.py`).
